課程概述 Course Description
       以細胞分子層次探討藥物作用之原理。讓修習本課程之研究生對於藥物作用之分子機制有深入之瞭解。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    修習本課程之研究生對於藥物作用之分子機制有深入之瞭解。    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Anticancer drugs in EGF receptor signaling2Epigenetic target therapies3G protein coupled receptors4From a gene to systemic regulation: example of CEBPs5Cell Division and Anti-Mitotic Drug6基因治療於人類遺傳性疾病的探討7Gene regulation8期中考9Epileptogenesis and antiepileptic drugs10記憶產生之分子機制11Telomeres and telomerase as targets for drug development12Inhibitor-of-apoptosis proteins (IAPs) and development of their inhibitors for anti-cancer therapy13Growth factors and tumor development14Post-translational modification of protein15Anti-inflammatory drugs in tissue inflammation and regeneration16期末考17自主學習18自主學習 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


